Name: Transcender Starship
About the game: Your mission is to capture as many data pods as possible and make it to the star within the 3:25 time limit. Maneuver the ship in front of the pod containers and fire the ship’s cannons to break them open. Once opened, the ship’s tractor beam will automatically recover the data pod. Your base score is determined by how quickly you make it to the star. You are awarded a bonus for each data pod that you recover along the way.
